Best staycation ever
I stayed at Intercontinental Danang for three days. The staff at the club lounge were incredibly friendly, and the food, hotel services, and amenities were all luxurious and excellent. There were also many monkeys around, but they weren't aggressive towards people, which was adorable. I can confidently say it was the best hotel I've ever stayed at. Throughout my stay, Steven, the club lounge manager, continuously checked if we were comfortable and if we needed anything, ensuring we had the best relaxation possible. He was extremely kind and always greeted us with a smile, which I appreciated. On the day of checkout, they gave us a monkey plush toy, which looked exactly like the long-tailed monkey I saw outside my room right before leaving. I was surprised and delighted by theâ€¦
