Le T wrote a review Feb 2024
Exquisite Experience at the Long Bar, Intercontinental Danang Resort
I recently had a visit to the Long Bar at Intercontinental Danang Resort, and it exceeded all expectations. The elegant ambiance, coupled with panoramic views of the ocean, creates a perfect setting for relaxation and socializing. The staff's hospitality, Nhi Vo and Lan Vu and others, was exceptional, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience. The mixologists at the Long Bar are true artisans, crafting cocktails that are both visually stunning and a delight to the palate. The diverse menu offers a range of options, from classic cocktails to innovative concoctions, all made with precision and flair. The attention to detail in the dÃ©cor and furnishings adds to the overall luxurious feel of the bar. The comfortable seating and subtle lighting contribute to a cozy atmosphere,â€¦
