Peihong W wrote a review Feb 2024
2 contributions
Intercontinental Da Nang is just like home!
The most beautiful resort we have ever been! The architecture is unique with a great mix of eastern and European elements. Staff are extremely professional, responsive and attentive! Food at the restaurants are all delicious but Citron is the best place for dining for our family. Lots of delicious Vietnamese dishes! Mai Huy served us a couple of times. He is warm, knowledgeable about the food and he is such a great photographer! Will definitely refer to friends and might come back again!
Dear peihongw2019, Thank you for sharing your wonderful experience at our resort. We are thrilled to hear that you found our resort to be the most beautiful one you have ever visited. Our team takes great pride in the unique architecture that combines Eastern and European elements, and we are delighted that it resonated with you. We appreciate your kind words regarding our staff. Providing professional, responsive, and attentive service is a top priority for us, and we are glad to hear that our team met your expectations in this regard. It is fantastic to know that you enjoyed the dining experience at our restaurants, particularly at Citron. We are pleased that our delicious Vietnamese dishes left a lasting impression on you and your family. We will pass along your compliments to Mai Huy for his warm service, knowledge about the food, and photography skills. Thank you for recommending our resort to your friends. We greatly appreciate your recommendation and thank you once again for choosing our resort. We look forward to welcoming you back soon. Warmest regards, Seif Hamdy General Manager
